"```sql\nSELECT account.account_id\nFROM client\nINNER JOIN disp ON client.client_id = disp.client_id\nINNER JOIN account ON disp.account_id = account.account_id\nWHERE client.birth_date = (SELECT MIN(birth_date) FROM client)\nGROUP BY client.client_id\nHAVING AVG(disp.account_id) = (SELECT MAX(avg_salary) FROM (SELECT AVG(disp.account_id) AS avg_salary FROM disp GROUP BY client_id) AS avg_table);\n```"